properties.description: Pro Series Black Triple-Function Combo Grill
properties.full_description: Get grilling done right with the Pit Boss pro series black triple-function combo grill. The only wood pellet grill and gas grill combo to deliver the flavor of wood with the ease of gas. Featuring more than 1200 sq. Ins. of cooking surface, the PB1100PSC1 is ready to bring all of your favorite meals to the backyard. 8-In-1 versatility allows you to smoke, bake, roast, braise, sear, grill, char-grill, or barbecue using 100% all-natural hardwood pellets or liquid propane. Simply adjust the slide-plate flame broiler and dial-in temperature control board. Then, create everything from slow-smoked brisket to flame-seared steak. The additional gas-powered side burner offers 10,000 BTU’s that’s perfect for warming side dishes, frying chicken, or simmering, boiling, and more. Additional features include a 180° to 500°F temperature range, 22-pound hopper, premium-gauge stainless steel build, porcelain-coated cast-iron cooking grates, two included stainless-steel meat probes, adjustable smokestack, three independent gas burners, locking caster wheels, grease management system, folding front shelf, and solid bottom shelf for extra storage.

properties.title: Pit Boss Pit Boss 1150 Pro Series Pellet Grill
properties.description: Pit Boss 1150 Pro Series Pellet Grill
properties.full_description: The Pit Boss pro series 1155 wood pellet grill gets grilling done right. Featuring a digital control board and advanced technology, the PB1150PS2 delivers even temperatures and more all-natural hardwood smoke than ever before. Enjoy perfectly cooked meals and unbeatable flavor. Plus, use the Pit Boss smoke it application combined with wireless and blue tooth compatibility to maximize your grilling experience, control temperature settings, monitor your grill’s meat probes, and more. With a 1,155 square inch cooking area, this massive grilling machine can easily serve a crowd. The PB1150PS2 comes equipped with a temperature range of 180° – 500°F and our patented simple slide-plate flame broiler. Pull a level to use indirect heat or push the lever allowing direct flame searing up to 1,000°F. Using fan forced convection cooking and 100% all-natural hardwood fuel this unit delivers great results however you choose to cook; sear, smoke, BBQ, roast, char-grill, braise, bake, and grill – all-in-one.
